### URI PARTS
Returns a component of a Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) string.

```esql
ROW my_url = "http://myusername:mypassword@example.org:80/foo.gif?key1=val1&key2=val2#fragment"
| EVAL my_url_domain = URI_PARTS(my_url, "domain")
```
